oji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b621703211713c8a6ca983e93e8df5b9ffe320eb","tid":507252,"uid":89240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T09:47:47.000Z","msg":"合理化煙幕"},{"pid":"f2ba3a0bae8d301d2ed6bc662d147522182b35e3","tid":507252,"uid":34023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>荃灣路德圍嗰兩間賣豆腐花都係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n荃灣又係平到爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果兩間豆腐花我成日行過去都會留意下<br />\n發覺佢地兩邊係輪住做<br />\n呢邊要排隊果陣，另一邊就無咩人<br />\n到另一邊有人龍，呢邊就無人<br />\n睇落都係各有各做<br />\n<br />\n人好得意<br />\n明明你平一蚊，我就會覺得好似啲質素差啲咁，明明都係垃圾<br />\n因為你比得起果一蚊差價吖嘛<br />\n一蚊可以食好啲點解唔比?<br />\n<br />\n所以最好大家同一價錢<br />\n我覺得咁樣買同賣都唔使咁諗得咁辛苦啦"},{"pid":"42ae6372b5fcdf67f2072455a4d3329fb51bb11e","tid":507252,"uid":5455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T10:37:13.000Z","msg":"行埋黎 行埋黎<br />\n<br />\n有次係個頭等人，個阿姐嘈到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e60fbbe7b3009c86a87ef25892026f9387b798","tid":507252,"uid":59909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行埋黎 行埋黎<br />\n<br />\n有次係個頭等人，個阿姐嘈到仆街&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n魚蛋燒賣 買一串 送一串 5蚊一大碗<br />\n煎釀三寶十蚊六件 行埋黎<br />\n<br />\n不停loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da70262b82044a05c0c188895122b1b2bc59f0d4","tid":507252,"uid":49316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T14:20:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一撚定係轉角街口個間<br />\n賣埋野飲個間<br />\n<br />\n另一間佢之前俾人訪問時當香港人係狗咁 <br />\n當大陸人係寶<br />\n買過一次 對住啲大陸人招呼好到 3-4個人一齊招呼個支那人<br />\n我就問左幾次話想買野食 冇人理<br /